one for an accented Iranian woman

00:07:40.760 --> 00:07:45.640
who has spent most of her life
in post-revolutionary Iran.

00:07:45.640 --> 00:07:50.840
A place not always imagined as
a dance-cultivating environment.

00:07:50.840 --> 00:07:53.440
In fact, it's largely
believed that all forms

00:07:53.440 --> 00:07:55.970
of dance are prohibited in Iran.

00:07:58.140 --> 00:08:02.280
