they were elderly Armenian women

00:08:02.280 --> 00:08:07.590
who taught me a variety of
dances including Caucasian,

00:08:07.590 --> 00:08:13.440 position:56%
[inaudible] Persian, as well as paso
doble, tango, cha-cha, and waltz,

00:08:13.440 --> 00:08:17.300
a peculiar repertoire
for a teenager.

00:08:17.300 --> 00:08:22.440
When Iraq was bombing Iran,
I was rehearsing dance.

00:08:22.440 --> 00:08:26.590
These classes inspired me and
really didn't cure my shyness.

00:08:26.590 --> 00:08:31.110
